<div class = "contain" style = "display:none">
<h2 class="title">Feature Selection for Your Social Preference Model</h2>
<hr class = "feature-hr">
<p class = "feature-text" >
  Whenever you open your company’s app and start driving, an in-app algorithm works to match
  you with potential customers in your given area. This algorithm has two main goals:
</p>
<ul class = "feature-list">
  <li class="feature-text">
    - Provide rides/deliveries to customers when needed
  </li>
  <li class = "feature-text">
    - Maximizing drivers’ amounts of trips on the system to maximize drivers’ earnings
  </li>
</ul>
<p class = "feature-text" >
 The boxes below contain features we believe your company’s algorithm
 uses to match drivers with incoming requests. Based on your experiences
 driving for your company, <b>please select any features that you believe your
 company’s algorithm should consider when matching drivers with requests.</b>
</p>
<div class="feature-image-block">
  <p class = "feature-text">
    For your selected features, please use the sliders on the right to determine
    how much importance you believe the algorithm should place on each factor. If there
    are features not listed below that you think the should algorithm use, please
    add your own at the bottom of the page.
    Please assign the level of importance to these additional features.
  </p>
  <%= image_tag ('Feature_Selection.png'), :class => "feature-selection-image" %>
</div>

<table class = "feature-table striped highlight" id = "feat">
    <thead>
     <th>  </th>
     <th>  </th>
    </thead>
    <% a = get_ranges_ai %>
    <% b = get_ranges_ai_2 %>
    <% counter = "" %>
    <% Feature.all.active.driver.added_by(current_user.id).order(:description).each do |f| %>
    <tr>

      <td>
        <% if  counter  == "" || f.description != counter %>
        <h5 class = "subheader"> <%= f.description %> </h5>
        <% end %>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="card ">
            <div class="card-content">
              <p class="feature-card-text"><%=f.name %></p>
              <form id = "range_form" action="#">
              <p class="range-field" style = "display: inline-block;">
                Importance <input type="text"  class = "weight" style = "border-bottom:none;width:7%;margin-right:10%;margin-top:0%;" id="textInput-<%=f.id%>" value="<%= b.pop %>" >
                <input type="range"  style = "width:60%;float:right;" id="test5-<%=f.id%>" min="0" max="100" value = "<%= a.pop %>" class="range-importance" onchange="updateTextInput(this.value, this.id);" />
              </p>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </td>
      <% if f.description == "Your Own Feature(s) - Continuous" or f.description == "Your Own Feature(s) - Categorical" %>
        <td id = "yof-<%=f.id%>" style = "cursor:pointer;font-weight:bold;font-size:2em;"> &times; </td>
      <% end %>
    </tr>
    <% counter = f.description %>
  <% end %>
</table>


